    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent care and mechanical integrity. This unit offers a refined driving experience, featuring a clean interior and a robust powertrain that has been thoroughly vetted by our service department. An ideal acquisition for the discerning buyer seeking a balance of performance and long-term value. Available for immediate inspection and delivery.",
