    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a wonderful example of a well-maintained daily driver that has been treated with care. The exterior finish still holds a deep, impressive shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a small hairline scratch near the trunk\u2014typical for a car of this age but hardly noticeable from a few feet away. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the seats show only light softening of the leather on the driver's side bolster, and every button, switch, and screen functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, the car is in great shape. It has a documented service history, including a recent comprehensive inspection and oil service. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, the brakes are firm, and the engine runs smoothly without any hesitation. It\u2019s a solid, dependable, and attractive car that is ready for the road immediately.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
