    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who needs a reliable daily driver. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs great, so I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll have a blast with it! I\u2019ve taken good care of it over the years, and I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
