    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed manual transmission. This example delivers visceral performance with a linear power band and a 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis dynamics are sharp, aided by the factory limited-slip differential and a well-sorted suspension geometry. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system refresh and subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural integrity of the platform. While it displays the minor cosmetic wear expected of a driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain remains robust with excellent compression and precise gear engagement. A true purist\u2019s machine ready for the open road.",
